sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant P as Player<br/>(mobile)
    participant W as WebClient<br/>oyna.pro
    participant B as Backend
    participant M as Middleware
    participant U as UE

    Note over P,U: QR join flow — игрок скан QR, попадает в сессию

    Note over U: QR code visible on game monitor<br/>(joinCode: 7AB-KZ9)

    P->>P: Open camera, scan QR
    P->>W: GET https://oyna.pro/join/7AB-KZ9

    alt User not logged in
        W->>P: Redirect to /login?return=/join/7AB-KZ9
        P->>W: POST /auth/login {email, password}
        W->>B: POST /api/v1/auth/login
        B-->>W: 200 {jwt}
        W->>P: Redirect back to /join/7AB-KZ9
    end

    W->>W: Display session info preview:<br/>"Join OYNA Laser Matrix?"<br/>"Cost: 10 minutes"<br/>"Your balance: 30 minutes"
    P->>W: Tap "Join"

    W->>B: POST /api/v1/users/me/join-session<br/>{joinCode: "7AB-KZ9"}
    B->>B: Find session by joinCode
    B->>B: Lock user row (FOR UPDATE)

    alt Session not found
        B-->>W: 404 {error: "SESSION_NOT_FOUND"}
        W->>P: Show error "Session not available"
    else Session full (6 players max)
        B-->>W: 409 {error: "SESSION_FULL"}
        W->>P: Show error "Room is full"
    else User already in session
        B-->>W: 409 {error: "ALREADY_JOINED"}
        W->>P: Show current session status
    else Insufficient balance
        B-->>W: 402 {error: "INSUFFICIENT_BALANCE", balance: 5, required: 10}
        W->>P: Show error + "Top up balance"
    else Session status != WAITING
        B-->>W: 409 {error: "SESSION_NOT_AVAILABLE", status: "ACTIVE"}
        W->>P: Show error "Session already started"
    else Success
        B->>B: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        B->>B: Find free slot (0..5)
        B->>B: INSERT MatchPlayer
        B->>B: INSERT Transaction (type=deduction, amount=10)
        B->>B: UPDATE user.balanceMinutes -= 10
        B->>B: COMMIT
        B-->>W: 200 {slot: 0, balanceAfter: 20}

        par Push to game
            B--)M: WS push: player_joined<br/>{sessionId, slot, userId, displayName}
            M--)U: player_joined
            U->>U: Show player name + color at slot
        and Notify player
            W->>P: Show "Joined slot 0"
            W->>P: Display "Waiting for operator to start..."
        end
    end

    Note over P,U: Player remains on phone screen until operator starts game
